Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.86,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Who is this? I've never seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:11.24,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Greetings! I'm Kinoto, the architect you \Nmost graciously requested on the telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:14.82,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,I'm here to appraise the cost of \Nthe renovation and repairs you mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.87,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I forgot I had called for an appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.33,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Heaven's Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:28.34,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I apologize for doing that so suddenly, \Nbut I've been trying to be more cautious lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:35.22,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,Note: "Yay! I got work! Gonna make some money! Kishibe Rohan seems rich, so I'm gonna make bank off him. Hopefully I can overcharge him a bit."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.02,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,Note: "I don't like anyone looking at my back."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:50.19,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,Note: "I won't let anyone see my back. I don't have acne, scars, or a tattoo,\N but I never want anyone to see my back! I wish I had a girlfriend. What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:32.63,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Born in 1970 and considered a first-class architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.13,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,His name is Kinoto Masazo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.22,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.97,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,He appears to be who he claims he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.72,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,He's neither a Stand user nor an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:41.81,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:53.70,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm unsure of what to make of this,\N but I suppose we all have our own strange fears and concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:57.78,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,At the very least, \NI see no reason to bar him from entering my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.45,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Though perhaps I should know better from that Rock, Paper, Scissors kid incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.41,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,To be safe, I'll write into him that he cannot attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:09.50,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Huh? Was I spacing out just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:13.42,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,No. But please, come in. Let's get to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:17.93,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.51,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,The room that caught fire is the one facing the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.27,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,We can't discuss this until you come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:26.56,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Oh, don't mind me! I'll follow behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:27.73,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:37.57,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Please, go on ahead!
Comment: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:41.53,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:48.92,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,513)\pos(141,890)\fs60}Episode 32: {\fs80} July 15th (Thursday) Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.83,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course I'll get away! It's simple. {This line and the next are in episode 31 and updated for blu-rays}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:52.25,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not like you guys have found Kira Yoshikage yet, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:56.42,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You haven't even seen my real face, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:00.68,Note,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Note: His name is a reference to the transmission tower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.47,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice how fake-sounding my name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.68,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,What kind of name is Kanedaichi Toyohiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.47,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Wh-What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.93,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Are you wearing some kind of mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:10.44,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I didn't waste my time thinking about leaving here without coming up with a solid getaway plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.48,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess this is goodbye forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Y-You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.32,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Please do not come in, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.45,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I have decided to remain inside this transmission tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?! What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:27.29,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,This entire ordeal arose from \Nmy discovery of the transmission tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:31.63,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,...and it was my idea to put\N myself at risk by transforming into the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.13,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I knew I could be of use to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.05,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I did it so that you would be proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.76,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Despite Okuyasu's insistence that I stay out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.76,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I brought this upon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.06,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Do not fear for my well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:50.27,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Compared to living in a spaceship, \Nit is quite spacious in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.27,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,You're a weird guy, but I respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.95,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Honestly though, I don't really care who stays here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.16,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's all the same as long as it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.28,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You can work out who stays here amongst yoursel{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.12,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who's staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:10.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's only one "goodbye" happening here! {present tense when it should be future}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.63,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,And it's the one we'll say to you once the three of us leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.21,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.21,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Since you cut the wire, \NI was able to restore it and climb right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.47,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Impossible... {Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.94,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mikitaka, think you can hold on for another ten seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:36.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Once I'm finished beating this asshole \Nback into the transmission tower, I'll heal you right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:39.11,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Don't fall, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.74,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Ain't happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:45.78,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I called what you did impossible earlier, but I was wrong...{Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.74,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I should have said it was impossibly stupid! {Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.17,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I just wanted to finally leave this transmission tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:56.25,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I never planned on killing anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:02.88,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,But now I'm gonna have to send you crashing back down \Nto the ground so I can get away, you impossibly stupid idiot!{Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.34,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.53,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Crazy Diamond...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.12,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Your Stand looks pretty strong up close, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:36.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,...do you think you stand a chance of laying even a single finger on me when I can get around this transmission tower with my eyes closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I'm guessing its effective range is no more than two meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.39,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What was that for? Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.90,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Josuke, move from that spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.15,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,He already used his knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.65,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,He cut into the transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That was a dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:16.37,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Good thing my Crazy Diamond is fast enough to defend itself from your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.46,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What's with the smirk, asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:23.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You happy I'm about to beat that smile off your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.93,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I know this transmission tower like the back of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:33.52,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I know exactly how to cut it to make\N the energy fly in whichever direction I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:39.65,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Like someone who has played \Nbilliards way too much, I know all too well! {wtf does this mean?}{I know this is probably an old comment, but he says billiards because shortly after he says this the energy from his attacks start bouncing around the tower like billiards balls.} {Do people who play billiars a lot know all too well? I think "I know all too well" is too vague considering the analogy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.27,Thoughts,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Billiards?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.65,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Jo{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.94,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:50.99,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You said your Crazy Diamond was fast enough to defend itself from my attacks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.20,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,But can you tell which direction they'll even come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.87,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I wonder how many shots I've fired off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.79,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,They're bouncing off the tower's beams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.55,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.46,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:05.80,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.80,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,From behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.43,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.94,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,That's why I called you impossibly stupid! {Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:24.19,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,That space alien or whatever was ready to stay here\N in the transmission tower forever. You should have let him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.74,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Then you wouldn't have needed to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.36,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,B-Both of his arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.95,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,He has no chance of defending himself \Nfrom the next attack like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.58,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Here it comes! This energy will finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.54,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's going right for your...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.54,Secondary,Josuke,0,0,0,,By the way, Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:45.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Did you see how many of his shots \NI was able to block with Crazy Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.88,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:51.30,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I think ya got four of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.93,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you just say "by the way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Four, huh? Well, that should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Four shots should be plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.44,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Earlier you said they were bouncing off the beams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:11.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You said your Stand's energy was bouncing around like billiard balls to attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.95,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say, Josuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.74,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,My Stand is Crazy Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:22.29,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm sure the old man from the photo already told you, \Nbut its ability is to restore damaged objects and energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.63,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Restore? It can restore things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.80,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,What exactly did it restore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:30.72,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Are you trying to imply you had\N the chance to restore something just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.01,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:40.39,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,He restored the deflected energy \Nand returned them to where they originated from!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:45.15,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Josuke, I believed you to be defeated, but your victory was assured all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.15,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I-Impossible... {Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:51.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I guess you really meant it was impossible after all!{Pun line}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.83,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.58,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I decided to live on the transmission tower since I couldn't stand other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:10.46,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,But the old guy in the photo convinced me that if I could trap even a single Stand user here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:16.10,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,...he would look after me in the outside world, \Nwhich is why I went along with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:20.52,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Please! Will you let me stay here in the transmission tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.64,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I never want to leave here ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.36,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I want to stay here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.61,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I'll never think of leaving the transmission tower ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.91,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}New Morioh Landmark: The Man Living on the Transmission Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:41.54,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bringing him salt or snacks will make him more than happy to take pictures with you, despite his preference to remain in solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:46.38,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's a bit shy, which is why he wears \Na mask and keeps his real name a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Anyway, that old guy in the photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Did he say anything else to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:54.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Like where his son, Kira Yoshikage, is?\N Or maybe something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:01.72,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Is there a Stand user named Koichi living here in Morioh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What did he say about Koichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:10.73,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Listen, the old guy in the photo just randomly mentioned him while he was talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:15.45,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I didn't ask many questions, \Nand he didn't go into detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.24,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Who cares?! What'd he say about Koichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.20,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,He said he was eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:29.84,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It sounded like the old photo guy \Nfinally figured out where his son, Kira Yoshikage, is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:35.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,He said this wasn't about protecting his son anymore, \Nand that he was preparing to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:40.18,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Then he mentioned this morning that \Na new Stand user eliminated another Stand user named Koichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.39,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.65,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Hmm... This is rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.94,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Whoa! Th-This door will cost at least 800,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.32,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Its design is highly reminiscent of doors \Nmade during the Victorian and Edwardian eras!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.41,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,The material appears to have come from England, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.78,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,This certainly won't be cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.66,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,I know he doesn't want anyone to see his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:09.42,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,...but was he doing this the entire way to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.04,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.59,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.96,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Drink before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.09,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.36,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I must remain in control...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.16,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Now isn't the time...
Comment: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:02.01,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Poor Koichi... I hope they find him safe and sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:16.61,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Fuck, he's gone! \NHe ain't at home or at school! He ain't anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.86,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Koichi! Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.03,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Where are ya, Koichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.20,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I ain't givin' up that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:29.20,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I'll find ya no matter what, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.17,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,And that's why we need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:36.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We need your incredible sense of smell\N and tracking abilities to help us find Koichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...Fungami Yuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:43.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,In exchange, I'll heal your injuries. It's a fair trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.89,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,A fair trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:50.31,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Don't fuck with me, Josuke! \NYou underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.56,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for doing this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:58.82,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I have too much pride to even {\i1}think{\i0} about helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.11,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I guess it was pointless to ask you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.20,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Well, see you around. \NCan't waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.70,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Wait, huh? You're giving up that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.37,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a sec, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.71,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can work something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.96,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Okay, fine! I'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.46,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,You're a tough one to bargain with, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:24.55,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I'm the only one losing out here if I let \Nmy tough guy act keep me from getting outta this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:33.14,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I can't show my girls any love like this, \Nand it's starting to make me feel worried and alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:39.07,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I'm pretty much where I was after I got in the accident,\N so I can't really hold it against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.90,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,So can'tcha just hurry up and heal me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.65,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,These injuries are driving me crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:47.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I just finished healing you with Crazy Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.53,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.13,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I gotta say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.55,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,...I am one devilishly handsome man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.51,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,To say I resemble a Michelangelo sculpture would be a huge understatement!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:10.14,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,But looking closer, \NI think my eyes are a bit droopier than before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.02,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Did your Stand really heal me up 100%?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't even start with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:18.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,More importantly, just how good is your sense of smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:23.90,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Good question... \NI mean, I don't want you to think of me like some hunting dog, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:31.16,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,To give you an idea, \NI can smell three girls walking down the hall right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.08,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Smells like Reiko, Akemi, and Yoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.79,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,They're my groupies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.92,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I can even tell that they came here from the pachinko parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.42,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Yutie Pie, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:49.30,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Ah, Yutie Pie! Our Yutie Pie is out of bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.30,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.10,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Are you all better, Yutie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.35,Main,All,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yutie Pie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.69,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Take it easy there, my lovely ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.23,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,It's Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.73,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.78,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Looking to get your ass kicked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.74,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Josuke and I are cool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.45,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,But more to the point, \Nyou three were just playing pachinko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.12,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.99,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.04,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I can smell the ass sweat on your skirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:19.54,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,The only reason I can think of for all three of you to \Nbe sitting on your asses for that long is to play pachinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.17,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Akemi, you got chocolate on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.59,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,You won at pachinko, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.63,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,You're right! You're so smart, Yutie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.47,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Here, they're for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:34.22,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,As you can tell... \NI'm the man I am today because of these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:37.06,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,You healed my injuries, so I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You don't want me to think of you like a hunting dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're way better than that, Fungami Yuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.32,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.82,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,The floor upstairs is also burnt, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.32,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,I'll appraise it as well, so please go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.33,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,What is with this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.08,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Why is he going to such lengths to hide his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.16,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,What will he do if I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.80,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,I-I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.38,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,All the trouble he's gone through to hide it \Nmakes me want to see it even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.84,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'll trick him into showing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.35,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Oh, my back... It's so itchy... {Apparently Rohan is Steely Dan now}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.85,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I just can't quite reach the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:23.52,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I apologize for asking this so soon after meeting you, but can you please scratch my back for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.32,Main,Kinoto,0,0,0,,Well... I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This is where we found Koichi's bag lying on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi's house is less than two minutes away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:50.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,How did this new Stand user manage to attack Koichi and take him away on his way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Nobody even saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.35,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.98,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,This deal of ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:07.86,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,It doesn't involve me fighting, does it?\N I just needed to track his scent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:12.07,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,You don't expect me to fight any enemies, right, Josuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.12,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Why are you asking that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.87,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,You're being followed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.37,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,...by that man over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.75,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I can smell Koichi's scent coming from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:32.13,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,He has something of Koichi's on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What? That guy over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.89,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wait! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:44.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You asshole! What did you do with Koichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:49.82,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,M-Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This is definitely my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.12,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,She's unconscious, but still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.70,Thoughts,Yuya,0,0,0,,Even watching from here, I couldn't tell what just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.75,Thoughts,Yuya,0,0,0,,When did he change into Josuke's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:09.04,Thoughts,Yuya,0,0,0,,I heard that Jotaro can stop time for two seconds,\N but this is nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.22,Thoughts,Yuya,0,0,0,,Jotaro couldn't just swap places\N with a random person out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:19.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If he had targeted me directly, \NI would have been satisfied just knocking him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but that asshole went after my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't forgive him for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Playing a trick like this is too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.11,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yuya! Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Where did that asshole disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:34.53,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,If you were touching him when he disappeared, how do you think I would know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.86,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,B-But... He's definitely still here, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.95,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,He's close! His scent is still strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.75,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Hmm... Fungami Yuya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.42,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,I'm surprised his sense of smell is this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:53.30,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,I expected to get caught once I started following him, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.05,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,I had every intention of bringing out Josuke's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.18,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,...so that I could observe him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.89,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Observe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.64,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,My Stand, Enigma, excels at observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:12.44,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Luckily, Enigma has already observed\N Hirose Koichi, as well as Josuke's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.78,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Sometimes he really pisses me off... {Line from episode 31}{Updated for blu-ray}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.91,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,I guess he won't mind if I eat his pudding, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.46,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Josuke! You really {\i1}were{\i0} still at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.21,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.68,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Every human being feels fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:53.44,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,There's no use trying to hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:59.40,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,The fear that lies deep within one's heart can never be erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.70,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,...no matter how hard they try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.91,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you? How did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.62,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,I've already figured it out in this short time watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:13.38,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,When you're afraid, you have a habit of swallowing your saliva, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:18.59,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Everyone has a subconscious sign \Nwhich reveals when they're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.43,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,A habit that only shows itself in the face of fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.18,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Did you not realize it until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.64,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Tell me who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.22,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,I won't give you any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.56,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.56,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Do I look like a burglar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:34.56,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,I don't want your money.\N In fact, I should be paying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:38.99,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Because right now, I'm having way too much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.78,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,I just love how much attention you're giving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:47.16,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,The attention you're giving me out of fear, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.55,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Oh? You swallowed again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:13.15,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,See? You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:16.31,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,It's a sure sign that you're afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:25.07,Main,Enigma,0,0,0,,Once the sign of your fear is known,\N my Enigma can complete its unavoidable attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:45.59,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,I turned Higashikata Tomoko and \NHirose Koichi into paper without a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:50.47,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,When I startled Koichi on his way to school, \Nhe revealed his sign in the form of blinking twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.18,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,I recognized it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:56.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yuya! I need you to tell me where his scent is coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:03.74,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,As tough as Higashikata Josuke is, I expected him to be afraid the moment his mother appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.70,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,But just like that, I know Josuke's sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:12.25,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Josuke bites his lower lip when he's afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:20.00,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Next time Josuke is afraid and shows that sign, my Enigma will eliminate him from this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:23.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yuya, you keep looking toward my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:28.47,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is it her jacket? Is there something inside her pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.35,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of Stand he has, \Nbut could it be in her pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.77,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Oh? Is he going to bite his lower lip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.06,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Come on, bite it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yuya, answer me! Is he in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.90,Thoughts,Enigma,0,0,0,,Damn! He isn't afraid enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:45.61,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,Josuke, I never promised to help you fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.61,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I only promised to track down your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:50.74,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous for me to help more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:57.37,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I accepted your deal since you healed my injuries, \Nbut only an idiot would put himself in danger for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:00.59,Main,Yuya,0,0,0,,I'm sorry man, but that guy is too fucking creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.22,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll just have to see for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's nothing here... Both pockets are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:11.51,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Except for this piece of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.94,Thoughts,Yuya,0,0,0,,The scent isn't coming from her pocket anymore... Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:21.65,Thoughts,Yuya,0,0,0,,Don't do it! Whatever you do, \N{\i1}do not{\i0} unfold that piece of paper!
